ing: 1 tablespoon milk, or more to taste
des: "I put this together when my apples and peanut butter addiction was at its peak. It's light, fluffy, and has a great peanut butter taste. Store in the refrigerator."
ins: Combine Greek yogurt, peanut butter, milk, cinnamon, nutmeg, red chile pepper, and salt in a bowl; beat with an electric mixer until light and fluffy.
